<p>The <em>Be My Guest</em> host is all about entertaining friends and family with fresh ingredients and bright flavours, so we’re taking a page from her recipe book and creating all kinds of yummy dishes this spring. Here are some of the host’s brightest and freshest spring recipes, from mains to desserts.</p>
<p>Looking for more inspiration? Be sure to watch new episodes of <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/tag/be-my-guest-with-ina-garten/"><em>Be My Guest With Ina Garten</em></a> starting Sunday, April 28 at 11:30AM ET/PT on Food Network Canada. Stream Food Network Canada with a STACKTV subscription. <a href="https://www.stacktv.ca/?utm_source=Corus&amp;utm_medium=Website&amp;utm_campaign=Food&amp;utm_content=BlogPosts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Try it free today.</a></p>
<p>Related: <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/article/spring-inspired-brunch-menu/">A Spring-Inspired Brunch Menu to Serve up This Weekend</a></p>


