><span class="gallery-slide-number-current">6</span>/<span class="gallery-slide-number-total">10</span></div><h2 class="gallery-slide-title">Crunchy Noodle Salad</h2><div class="gallery-slide-description"><p>Add a little crunch to your spring noodle salad with fresh peppers and sugar snap peas a la Ina Garten. This recipe starts with spaghettini noodles and transforms into something special thanks to peanut butter, ginger, sesame, and rice wine vinegar.</p>


