y-slide-number"><span class="gallery-slide-number-current">8</span>/<span class="gallery-slide-number-total">10</span></div><h2 class="gallery-slide-title">Tomato Carpaccio </h2><div class="gallery-slide-description"><p>There’s nothing like biting into a fresh tomato, and this recipe delivers that feeling with every forkful. The trickiest part is making the creamy and salty dressing, but with fresh ingredients and a food processor, you’ll enjoy this spring bite in no time.</p>
