ide-number-current">9</span>/<span class="gallery-slide-number-total">10</span></div><h2 class="gallery-slide-title">Roasted Salmon Tacos</h2><div class="gallery-slide-description"><p>Why eat <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/recipe/grilled-tequila-lime-fish-tacos/">fish tacos</a> when you can serve up salmon tacos instead? Freshly roasted (or grilled) salmon pairs perfectly with warm corn tortillas, homemade slaw and mashed avocados, offering a tasty preview of warmer <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/tag/summer/">summer</a> fare ahead.</p>


