lass="gallery-slide-number"><span class="gallery-slide-number-current">10</span>/<span class="gallery-slide-number-total">10</span></div><h2 class="gallery-slide-title">Lemon Cake</h2><div class="gallery-slide-description"><p>What better way to top off a delicious meal than with a delightful spring <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/tag/dessert/">dessert</a>? Nothing says spring like lemons, so this lemon cake is always a favourite. It’s also super easy to make, and leftovers can be a decadent <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/tag/breakfast/">breakfast</a> the next morning. In our book, that makes this Ina Garten recipe an all-around win.</p>


